==Indonesian==

===Verb===
'''duduk'''  {{intransitive}}

# to [[sit]] down
# to be [[sitting]]/[[seated]]
#* '''duduk''' [[bersila]]
#: to '''sit''' cross legged
#* '''duduk''' [[perkara]]
#: the [[way]] [[matters]] [[stand]]
#* [[ruang]] '''duduk'''
#: a '''sitting''' [[room]]
#* [[tempat]] '''duduk'''
#: a chair

===Usage notes===
"[[Silakan]] '''duduk'''" translates to "Please sit down" or "Please take a seat".

